dct_description_sm: Map shows important buildings, churches, schools, cemetaries, soccer fiels, roads, area limits, rivers, railroads, water tanks, and swimming pools. Relief shown by shading and spot heights. "Esta hoja ha sido preparada por métodos fotogramétricos, con fotografías tomadas en 1984, por el Instituto Geográfico Nacional Ingeniero Pablo Arnoldo Guzmán del Ministerio de Obras Públicas." "Mayo 1985."
